item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossy)】MP3 - Britney Spears - In the Zone (Fresh Edition)
item.description:
​

In the Zone (Fresh Edition) is a fanmade remix album of songs by Britney Spears. The majority of the compilation features tracks from Spears' 2003 album In the Zone, with additional tracks from 2004's Greatest Hits: My Prerogative and 2005's B in the Mix: The Remixes.

Using stems of the original tracks, fans created extended mixes of each song, which were labeled as "fresh" mixes.


1. Me Against the Music (Rishi Rich's Desi Kulcha Remix) [feat. Madonna]
2. I Got That Boom Boom (feat. Ying Yang Twins)
3. Showdown
4. Breathe on Me
5. Early Mornin'
6. Toxic
7. Outrageous
8. Touch of My Hand
9. The Hook Up
10. Brave New Girl
11. Everytime
12. My Prerogative
13. Do Somethin'
14. And Then We Kiss (Junkie XL Remix)
